    {
        "content": "<p>I've just pushed a file <code>Mathlib.Algebra.DirectSum.SumLEquivProd</code> full of stuff that should be moved to other files and which has an isomorphism between a direct sum indexed by a sum type &amp; a product of direct sums, i.e.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">noncomputable</span> <span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">sumLEquivProd</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ια</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">AddCommMonoid</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ιβ</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">AddCommMonoid</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">β</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ια</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">Module</span> <span class=\"n\">k</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ιβ</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Module</span> <span class=\"n\">k</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">β</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">⨁</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ια</span> <span class=\"bp\">⊕</span> <span class=\"n\">ιβ</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">Sum.elim</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"n\">β</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">≃ₗ</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">⨁</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ια</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">×</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">⨁</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ιβ</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">β</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"bp\">...</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>at the end, which is hopefully what was needed for decomposition into irreducibles</p>",
